        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><strong>No Alternatives to Detention for Illegals Act of 2022</strong></p> <p>This bill prohibits the Department of Homeland Security (DHS) from enacting any program that provides alternatives to detention for a non-U.S. national (<em>alien</em> under federal law) who is in DHS custody and housed at an immigration detention center.<br> </p>]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
